source.name: Post Secondary Universe Survey 2010 - Directory Information
source.description: This file contains directory information for every institution in the 2010 IPEDS universe. Includes name, address, city, state and zipcode. Identifies institutions as currently active, institutions that participate in Title IV federal financial aid programs for which IPEDS is mandatory. It also includes variables derived from the 2010 Institutional Characteristics survey, such as control and level of institution, highest level and highest degree offered and carnegie classifications.
